{"tid":304383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［土地問題］兩高中生直接在卡啦OK啪啪啪片段被瘋傳","createTime":"2017-07-01T00:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T04:24:07.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aee7c5146dca1012c15b6982e9c36180d69e902d","tid":304383,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T00:09:24.000Z","msg":"這對情侶真是太開放了....，竟然就在卡拉OK的包廂內啪啪啪了起來，被隔壁間的顧客全都錄。<br />\n日本網友TOKYOREDRUM在《推特》分享影片指出，他日前去室內遊樂場ROUND1消費的時候，看到隔壁的高中生情侶在包廂內啪啪啪，於是就拿手機拍下影片，期間工作人員經過兩三次，都沒發現裡面兩人在啪啪啪，原PO還語重心長的發文說「看了影片後，知道是男同性戀在啪啪啪的人有多少呢」。<br />\n知道這驚人事實後，網友紛紛留言「看手臂好像真的都男的....」、「兩個八成是棒球社的吧」、「腐女子大喜」、「┌（┌ ＾o＾）┐ホモォ」，也有網友看了房間布置後，猜「是在平塚市的那一間嗎？」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170701/1151885/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170701%2F1151885%2F&d=go6WyNedYY7arn2l4y41654f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1d9b6bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170701/1151885/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/080841_4618e7f52cbe4fa7d7b91533f5a36fb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F080841_4618e7f52cbe4fa7d7b91533f5a36fb9.jpg&h=03a05f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瘋傳又無連登份"},{"pid":"1ebbcb2852e67830dea5b7d3eb7316fd300b3ebc","tid":304383,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T00:17:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b719733387b1e0223560f50a309a1ddfa95e16c","tid":304383,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"原片一樣乜都睇唔到<br />\n都唔知做咩打格"}]}